    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically robust 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six. This naturally aspirated powerplant utilizes individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure Double VANOS variable valve timing system to deliver a linear power band and an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is routed through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a factory-calibrated limited-slip differential. The chassis exhibits excellent torsional rigidity, with recent attention paid to the rear subframe mounting points and trailing arm bushings. This unit retains its original suspension geometry, offering the communicative steering and balanced polar moment of inertia that defines the platform. A solid, high-performance driver\u2019s car for the purist.",
